Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.42,0:00:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有意見嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
