Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.54,0:01:52.25,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,480)}#08 能治癒妹妹悲傷的人 是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.54,0:01:52.25,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(480,480)\3c&HF2C855&\bord8}#08 能治癒妹妹悲傷的人 是妹妹
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an1}真的沒弄錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an1}末續也是白夜和真白的同族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是真的 白夜也這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣看來感覺你們的族人也很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不是唷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很少的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是因為能夠隱蔽生活的山越來越少
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才有人下山和城裡人混在一起生活的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(651,260,755,304,100,2100)\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\shad0}驗證1    {\c&H4C30B1&}UFO是存在的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為城市既方便又有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 所以看電視的時候要離遠一點哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是同族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但好像也不是真白和白夜認識的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}完全不認識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概生活在我們不知道的其他地區的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}意料之外的相遇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是呢 而且對方似乎也不知道和我們是同族
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是這樣 感覺也真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是同族也不可能跟那傢伙做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或許世界充滿了不可思議的事情只是我們沒有發現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吧 可能就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比如外星人 UMA什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 不是說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續和真白他們是同族這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是對姐姐大人保密比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在學生會也會經常見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了嘛 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘…秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 秘密？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅…對我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}隱瞞著什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什麼事！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是胸部又變大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}上個月的胸圍尺寸應該是八十…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是我也會有一兩個秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也會有不能告訴姐姐大人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這 這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}叛逆期嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能夠治癒妹妹的悲傷的 只有妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這啥歪理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天因為紅緒的關係遇到了讓我很討厭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個叫末續的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來找碴 要我在紅緒的稱呼後面加上「大人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然會因為我引發爭執…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}罪孽深重的我
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續木葉 開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仔細回想 我在那位妹妹面前大喊大叫了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也許已經告訴紅緒大人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊～ 這樣我要怎麼去見紅緒大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有 那個小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然和紅緒大人一起洗 洗…洗澡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過 小不點他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的是我的同族嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 那個男生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從剛才開始就露出各種表情真是忙碌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 仁子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.48,0:05:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}取材現在才正要開始唷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發給小紅的問卷也該去回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…仁子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是考慮一下別的取材比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯…啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是紅緒大人最新的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想不想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去下新聞部的活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 仁子醬！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不會告訴別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 我會保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 那個 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼一回事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個人大喊大叫還有埋怨真白的事我會替你保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感激我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哦呵呵呵呵呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被抓到把柄了啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然還是保密比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰媽媽也這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也已經察覺末續是你們的同族了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感…覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺嗎
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HC79321&\fs50\pos(1042,466)\shad0\bord4}\N稍\N有\N遲\N鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\pos(162,288)\c&H8F633E&\shad0\bord4}\N相\N當\N遲\N鈍
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去問小紅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果太過糾纏而被討厭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我會很傷心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經被討厭了所以沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.13,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 你沒被打擊到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是從小紅小時候就像好姐妹一樣在一起玩耍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐妹之間也會有秘密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.22,0:06:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要不然就是對纏人的紅緒感到厭惡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼可能會有這種事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這自信是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}秘密…秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和真白碳說了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 難道是打算秘密舉辦派對之類的給我驚喜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是有多樂觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 對姐姐的秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也許是…男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 不是妹妹而是男孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}姊姊大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是弟弟嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你混亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 是弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}男孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說起來 最近都沒有一起洗過澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 無論如何都可以當做證據的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}胸前那兩粒凸起……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不可能是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}絕不可能
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 如果是扶他的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以 我可以接受的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是男朋友的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且也有未婚夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那件事對我有什麼值得隱瞞的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道已經超越那一線了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我沒有說到那種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牽手了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那點事就允許他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 就連我最近都沒有牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}通常都不會牽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之不可能什麼事都告訴紅緒你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒也不可能什麼都對小紅說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說出來會被討厭的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}唉呀 還算是有自知之明呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}騙人的騙人的 絕對有什麼地方搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}那個可愛的小紅居然會對我隱藏秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.08,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}Oh my god 絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在為世界擔憂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}補考也通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好幸福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 鯛魚燒而已居然有這麼多種類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好想知道桃子口味的鯛魚燒是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是還是不要冒險…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 但是奶油 栗子 巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 御好燒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請給我一個紅豆的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬 氣喘吁吁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我也選個紅豆餡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}熱量好像也很低
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 這也還有三百大卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來 給你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 關係真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其實不是那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我喜歡御好燒味的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以當飯吃
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在想調查問卷做好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 那下次見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又是那個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…沒能果斷拒絕她的我也有錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尺寸怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}腰圍正好了但是臀部好緊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用鬆緊帶的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個將來會用到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}確實在老太婆裡面很有人氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}鬆緊帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅很在意屁股大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幹 幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是剛好來買東西的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅的屁股大不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又沒說小紅的屁股大有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅不適應被採訪之類的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你放棄做這種事我會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉了 請忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好隨便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個人只有行動力才像是新聞部的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起 都怪我不會拒絕別人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用在意啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大野同學看起來是一個不講清楚就無法明白的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良意外的是個說話很乾脆的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？ 我也是個很直率的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This is a pen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個是巨乳嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是巨乳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別說了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.51,0:11:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 惹人生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然直接上不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這種程度 能幹的記者是不會放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 聯繫一下木葉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅是天使 那絕對是騙人的騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 仁子醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個啊 紅緒的大人的妹妹小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像啊 很在意屁股很大的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等…對不起我先出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是知道什麼我再告訴你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹的屁股大什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好像整體上有點肉的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在這一點上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我胸部屁股都很小很苗條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有在意過哪裡胖這種事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果要問這樣算不算好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}倒也確實不是好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和末續同學能友好相處的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們是同族嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易偶然相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能和睦相處的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:12:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她說了我是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最重要的 她是紅緒的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那裡才是重點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}首先 先確認那個小不點她們是不是我的同族才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然仁子醬被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對我可沒有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不會是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看中紅緒大人才混進紅緒大人家裡面的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人也被騙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有這一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}垃圾倒完了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學站在走廊上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是找誰有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個是…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊 你那眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有話找你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}屋頂可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也去比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹就請你不要去了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8F633E&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs50\pos(226,528)\bord4\shad0}\N強\N硬\N不\N起\N來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那兩位是朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}末續同學和真白一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和普通人有點不一樣的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良看起來呆呆的其實很敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 再怎麼敏銳也有限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再深入惹出麻煩可就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 就是那種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去看看狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偷窺的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.44,0:14:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.94,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有不會被察覺到的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 自信滿滿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對小不點認真太不成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那兩個怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是為了爭奪我的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}夠了請你回來工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}屋頂就好 話是這麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是北風好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}文件都成堆了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不趕快處理掉我會很頭疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然不是去看真白碳和末續的情況了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不就是很想去的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去回收在地下城全滅的隊友的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能編個像樣點的謊話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}換個地方吧x2
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說到叫人出來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}體育館後面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳 末續
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊勒 不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是同族啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看起來確實是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你做的不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.31,0:17:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算是同族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.85,0:17:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}居然做出混進紅緒大人的家裡這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬和白夜同學都好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我果然還是去看看情況吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}從目前為止的發展來看也不覺得氣氛能有多融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是白夜也被捲進去造成麻煩了可就……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.26,0:18:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小～～～紅～～呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吶 吶 真白碳和末續好像是一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.19,0:18:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.98,0:18:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦 還是別說多餘的話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這跟姐姐大人一點關係沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這跟姐姐大人一點關係沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點關係也沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一～點～關～係～也～沒～有～哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒～有～哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒～有～哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒～有～哦～～～～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 是…是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟姐姐大人一丁點關係都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.15,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一點關係也沒有的紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也沒在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 你別哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用哭的太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明跟我一丁點關係都沒有的說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那麼說也太失禮了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟我沒關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的第七感告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的 這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不可能的 不可能的 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.66,0:19:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}因為我可是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 你趕快過來看看這些文件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}覺醒了第七感的紅緒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要吃巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你這小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你對真白做什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是說她跟紅緒大人住在一起太狡猾了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.23,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼嘛 弄得好像我是壞人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道說你也是以紅緒大人為目標？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊 說中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然你們是為了紅緒大人才到這個城市的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還利用自身能力跟紅緒大人同居
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}羡慕死…不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.09,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是很狡猾不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以說啊 為什麼會變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來這裡是因為很擔心白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜也跟紅緒沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}竟然不懂的紅緒大人的優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等…咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底在說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}既然你對紅緒大人不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點呆呆的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是我喜歡的型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是失禮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同族的男孩子很難遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是遇上了就一定要先佔有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}佔有？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜明明說過不會被發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}跟我結婚吧
