Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不對是F罩杯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.05,0:23:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們說啥呢！？
